          {
            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 127084,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Websites and apps like the one below regularly need to perform the same task over and over.</p><webview version=\"2\" content=\"&lt;!doctype html&gt;&#xA;&lt;html&gt;&#xA; &lt;head&gt;&#xA;  &lt;style&gt;&#xA;   body {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;    height: 275px;&#xA;    font-size: 16px;&#xA;    margin: 0 auto;&#xA;    background-color: #F0F8FF;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   button {&#xA;    background-color: darkBlue;&#xA;    border: none;&#xA;    border-radius: 8px;&#xA;    color: white;&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;    text-decoration: none;&#xA;    display: inline-block;&#xA;    font-size: 14px;&#xA;    padding: 6px 12px;&#xA;    margin: 0 12px 0 0;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   h2 {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   #playerList {&#xA;    text-align: left;&#xA;   }&#xA;  &lt;/style&gt;&#xA; &lt;/head&gt;&#xA; &lt;body&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img height=180 src=&quot;https://mimo.app/i/volume-icon.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;  &lt;button onclick=&quot;increase()&quot;&gt;Increase volume&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p id=&quot;container&quot;&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;   &lt;script&gt;&#xA;    var volume = 0;&#xA;    &#xA;    function increase() {&#xA;     document.getElementById(&quot;container&quot;).innerHTML =&#xA;      &quot;Volume increased!&quot;;&#xA;     var s = document.getElementById('container').style;&#xA;     s.display = &quot;block&quot;;&#xA;     s.opacity = 1;&#xA;     (function fade() {&#xA;      if ((s.opacity -= .1) &lt; 0) s.display = &quot;none&quot;;&#xA;      else setTimeout(fade, 150);&#xA;     })();&#xA;    }&#xA;   &lt;/script&gt;&#xA; &lt;/body&gt;&#xA;&lt;/html&gt;\" /></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Intro 2",
            "id": 127085,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Instead of creating lots of different code, websites use <strong>functions</strong> to group related code and perform the task in one place.</p><webview version=\"2\" visible-if=\"always\" content=\"&lt;!doctype html&gt;&#xA;&lt;html&gt;&#xA; &lt;head&gt;&#xA;  &lt;style&gt;&#xA;   body {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;    height: 275px;&#xA;    font-size: 16px;&#xA;    margin: 0 auto;&#xA;    background-color: #F0F8FF;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   button {&#xA;    background-color: darkBlue;&#xA;    border: none;&#xA;    border-radius: 8px;&#xA;    color: white;&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;    text-decoration: none;&#xA;    display: inline-block;&#xA;    font-size: 14px;&#xA;    padding: 6px 12px;&#xA;    margin: 0 12px 0 0;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   h2 {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   #playerList {&#xA;    text-align: left;&#xA;   }&#xA;  &lt;/style&gt;&#xA; &lt;/head&gt;&#xA; &lt;body&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img height=180 src=&quot;https://mimo.app/i/volume-icon.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;  &lt;button onclick=&quot;decrease()&quot;&gt;Decrease volume&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p id=&quot;container&quot;&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;   &lt;script&gt;&#xA;    let volume = 0;&#xA;    &#xA;    function decrease() {&#xA;     document.getElementById(&quot;container&quot;).innerHTML =&#xA;      &quot;Volume decreased!&quot;;&#xA;     let s = document.getElementById('container').style;&#xA;     s.display = &quot;block&quot;;&#xA;     s.opacity = 1;&#xA;     (function fade() {&#xA;      if ((s.opacity -= .1) &lt; 0) s.display = &quot;none&quot;;&#xA;      else setTimeout(fade, 150);&#xA;     })();&#xA;    }&#xA;   &lt;/script&gt;&#xA; &lt;/body&gt;&#xA;&lt;/html&gt;\" /></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Function",
            "id": 127086,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>To begin grouping related code, we start by coding the keyword <code>func</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"func\" class=\"keyword\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"4\" /></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to type <code>func</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Function name",
            "id": 127087,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Next comes the function's name in camel case, like <code>greetUser</code>, followed by parentheses, <code>(</code> and <code>)</code>.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"func\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greetUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"5\" endIndex=\"14\" /><option startIndex=\"14\" endIndex=\"15\" /><option startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"16\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>greetUser</code>, followed by <code>(</code>, and finally <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Braces",
            "id": 127088,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Braces <code>{</code> and <code>}</code>, mark out the code block that belongs to the function.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"func\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greetUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"17\" endIndex=\"18\" /><option startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"22\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>{</code>, followed by <code>}</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Between braces",
            "id": 127089,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>The code we want to group together goes between the braces. This function groups two related <code>print()</code> statements.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"func\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greetUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Good morning Anna&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome back&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"53\" /><option startIndex=\"53\" endIndex=\"69\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>print</code>, followed by <code>(\"Welcome back\")</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Calling the function",
            "id": 127090,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>To run the code, we need to <strong>call</strong> the function. We do that by coding its name followed by parentheses, like <code>greetUser()</code>.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"func\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greetUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Good morning Anna&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome back&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"greetUser()\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"73\" endIndex=\"84\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Good morning Anna\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Welcome back\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to type <code>greetUser()</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
